      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <code class="language-css">.margin{-edge}{-amount}</code>
          </td>
          <td>
            <ul>
              <li>
                Modify the margin of an element. Left+right edge combined is <code>x</code>, top+bottom edges combined
                is <code>y</code>.
              </li>
